[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    193[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Suggested fix:** Add a brief note in the Prerequisites or after the architecture diagram: "The network path from on-premises imaging equipment to the S3 landing zone must be encrypted in transit. Options: (1) AWS Direct Connect with MACsec encryption for dedicated, low-latency connectivity; (2) Site-to-Site VPN for encrypted tunnel over public internet; (3) A DICOM gateway appliance (on-prem) that TLS-encrypts and forwards to an S3 Transfer Acceleration endpoint. Direct Connect is preferred for production radiology AI workloads due to consistent latency requirements (the 3-8 second end-to-end target assumes low-latency cloud ingress)."
